{"tid":252102,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"姑娘同空中侍應算唔算最低賤既職業?","createTime":"2017-05-21T12:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T02:29:12.000Z","uid":93141,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aaeae4fa46d5f734496ba1e12fc98ebf657cfaf2","tid":252102,"uid":93141,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:57:40.000Z","msg":"姑娘同空中侍應一樣咁濕鳩.<br />\n兩者都係女人環境下做奴工,所以出好多八婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩者都好鍾意乜鳩都呻一餐,明明條路自己揀,講到好似天下大伏咁.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老屎忽文化又重,新人後生女靚過你已經係死罪,入職要比老屎忽玩一餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明係為左錢/周圍飛先揀份工,又鍾意包裝到好似自己好有夢想咁,係咁有夢想就唔駛成日呻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後兩者都鍾意搭上比佢地搵得多既同事(醫生/機師),兩個職業最終目的就係搵碼頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e970e8a357315fad0832866ff19b48450ddeb3","tid":252102,"uid":4531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:59:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e78e2003351a2a5a77247fbc6eccdb1b86e61231","tid":252102,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:08:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3296bb6f68cf1dad9b04c3d3c8e0a252c66c86f8","tid":252102,"uid":65818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:14:38.000Z","msg":"姑娘唔計正式護士<br />\n咁你就成立<br />\n<br />\n正式果啲要港大中大<br />\n起碼有努過<br />\n真心不是雞<br />\n<br />\n空姐就全部都是雞<br />\n食過唔少<br />\n當去公廁"},{"pid":"da17fece1f229242307c525af7654485308d7fb3","tid":252102,"uid":113776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:18:07.000Z","msg":"正皮，上一頁"},{"pid":"e698f296c8c6ff5817b365a4047c0df61d05f675","tid":252102,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:18:15.000Z","msg":"姑娘閒閒地都要讀三四年專業課程考牌<br />\n你搵空姐呢啲飛機侍應黎比?"},{"pid":"c0045be4876b08c6fe7b50232cddeb98e43276a1","tid":252102,"uid":93141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:27:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>姑娘唔計正式護士<br />\n咁你就成立<br />\n<br />\n正式果啲要港大中大<br />\n起碼有努過<br />\n真心不是雞<br />\n<br />\n空姐就全部都是雞<br />\n食過唔少<br />\n當去公廁</blockquote><br />\n大學護士先最多垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而文憑護士謙虛少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我港大見到班nursing好多掛著玩,份人又西,唔覺得佢地會對病人多幾多heart<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n護士做雞的確少過空姐好多,但係性格一樣咁差都稱不上好女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0bd5cbe87b6c96e1172fe20166917ecade7af71","tid":252102,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:30:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>姑娘閒閒地都要讀三四年專業課程考牌<br />\n你搵空姐呢啲飛機侍應黎比?</blockquote><br />\n性格,本質呢d野讀書考牌都改變唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做教畜都要讀4年本科+1-2年pg啦,咪又係咁大班教畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b92aaa7a83ebe15a026eeec9229677378c697ee","tid":252102,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d022fe0465281a890c8c5890b04b12cbb3eee8","tid":252102,"uid":36014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:42:15.000Z","msg":"護士一開波30K 都低賤？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59578c5d12a38335a389b1277ea49851481ad8b1","tid":252102,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:47:35.000Z","msg":"正評，上一頁"},{"pid":"52bcc5db6830d4f2e77ed3c755f6d1cd4dcc82e8","tid":252102,"uid":71462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:49:32.000Z","msg":"住咗半個月院<br />\n發覺d姑娘都幾好脾氣 幾有禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39638815b64c2e68ff555930e0b292db448ed625","tid":252102,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:51:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>護士一開波30K 都低賤？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講緊個職業性質同埋佢地為人,唔係社經地位.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbffd3a6fb60d596e39269be2b86bb04f3667b83","tid":252102,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:53:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住咗半個月院<br />\n發覺d姑娘都幾好脾氣 幾有禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n私家會好好多既,公立遇到好既就幾生修到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n始終要搵食嘛,而且仲有一班大財主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過好黑暗,私家而家多數齋請後生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aec9e719276c237cdac11f370510982ef6e9314","tid":252102,"uid":44783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:55:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>護士一開波30K 都低賤？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講緊人格呀, 有錢冇品大有人在<br />\n做雞一日做3,4個鐘都唔止30K 啦<br />\n個腦唔係淨係得錢先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6a10f02d7c5cacb568ed694d00e7c78851912e","tid":252102,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:02:16.000Z","msg":"想聽返姑娘同空中侍應既意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7579ffa6604f5f8b656066c2e7a61019d9596492","tid":252102,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:04:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>護士一開波30K 都低賤？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講緊人格呀, 有錢冇品大有人在<br />\n做雞一日做3,4個鐘都唔止30K 啦<br />\n個腦唔係淨係得錢先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講人格嘅話 保險狗敦倫金先最低賤"},{"pid":"7354addbc1d1a024ef0558302f434c26b10c9c3e","tid":252102,"uid":30535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:13:24.000Z","msg":"八唔八婆應該係與生俱來，唔太關工作環境事嘅"},{"pid":"4b8ffb0245a8e177a0eedf4e75528c41549d96a3","tid":252102,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:17:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>護士一開波30K 都低賤？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講緊人格呀, 有錢冇品大有人在<br />\n做雞一日做3,4個鐘都唔止30K 啦<br />\n個腦唔係淨係得錢先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講人格嘅話 保險狗敦倫金先最低賤</blockquote><br />\n佢地係地底泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係佢地應該已經唔算正當職業,全部都係詐騙集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e26f4494e9da31f42d5516fc7d3c68ec8c95d4","tid":252102,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:27:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>八唔八婆應該係與生俱來，唔太關工作環境事嘅</blockquote><br />\n我覺得有唔同比例<br />\n例如醫生,工程,廚師,會計,設計呢種就比人感覺少d八婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而服務性越大/女性比例越大,八婆比例就越高.應該係為左鬧班客?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f0736f7df0466876e70ed8aacf540822313591","tid":252102,"uid":44783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:29:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>護士一開波30K 都低賤？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講緊人格呀, 有錢冇品大有人在<br />\n做雞一日做3,4個鐘都唔止30K 啦<br />\n個腦唔係淨係得錢先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講人格嘅話 保險狗敦倫金先最低賤</blockquote><br />\n佢地係地底泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係佢地應該已經唔算正當職業,全部都係詐騙集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾岩聽"}]}